{"tid":1974992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[幫推]觀塘金龍冰室極有機會有帶菌者逗留過","createTime":"2020-04-16T08:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T08:53:00.000Z","uid":312362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18083387e634bea4f175048244bf99e4e22960b6","tid":1974992,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"話說我今朝頭早去呢間冰室食野<br />\n期間有一名<span style=\"color: red;\">帶隔離手帶</span>嘅女人入黎食野<br />\n個位女人隻眼係腫曬 懷疑佢有可能<span style=\"color: red;\">發燒</span><br />\n但就未見有員工幫佢度體溫<br />\n而家我極度懷疑間餐廳/食客有受感染嘅機會<br />\n屌柒你好心有病要隔離就咪撚死出街害人啦<br />\n大家見到自己執生唔好去附近個頭<br />\nSorry for而家先講"},{"pid":"16b01c841ac09b7d031237844543eba3a1b26c0c","tid":1974992,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"求幫推"},{"pid":"3b8ce65900535a0486077941d917bd8c175b6fc7","tid":1974992,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeca13437e50e87ab176f21152a54d283bdd737","tid":1974992,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cbbfeb3a5249b8d3051dbe8efefcbf5fe9bfd0","tid":1974992,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />